WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.500
Hello! Today I'll show you how to rent a power bank by paying with a credit card.

00:05.500 --> 00:10.500
Scan the station's QR code — you'll be redirected to our website.

00:10.500 --> 00:17.000
On the site, tap "Agree and rent" and log in with your phone number.

00:17.000 --> 00:21.000
Tap "Go" and fill in the captcha.

00:24.500 --> 00:28.500
After the captcha, you'll receive a code by SMS on your phone.

00:31.000 --> 00:34.000
Then create your password.

00:35.000 --> 00:42.000
Once you've received the code, created your password and logged in, you'll be sent to the payment tab.

00:42.000 --> 00:45.000
Select the "Credit card" option.

00:45.000 --> 00:52.000
Tap "Add" and enter your credit card details.

00:52.000 --> 00:59.000
After confirming the payment, take the power bank and pick the cable you want to use.

01:00.000 --> 01:04.000
Connect it to your phone and press the power button on the power bank.

01:06.000 --> 01:08.000
Done — your phone is now charging.

01:08.000 --> 01:15.000
After returning the power bank, any unused balance will be refunded to your card within 48 hours.
